name: THE ARTIST LOOKING AT THE ART
description: I´ve been obsessively manipulating old photos and videos.  Questioning what or who creates value in art? How often I feel compelled by other artists work? Life is a perfect marketplace.  In the image my friend Eli (@neomlei) looking at Las Damas de Aviñón.  MOMA, 2019.  2048 x 2048 mp4
